                                                                                                Appendix E—Resources

                                                                                                The lists below provide examples of resources that may be helpful in better understanding telework and
                                                                                                remote access security. The NIST Special Publications identified below, along with many others, can also
                                                                                                be accessed via http://csrc.nist.gov/publications/PubsSPs.html.



